<br>
That part of the strategy I understand. It works well. But I have read some posts here about how uber mobs always tend to smack you for max damage anyways, regardless of your AC. So does that mean the main tank should be using HP gear instead? Should I use the defensive discipline? Before the nerf, I always did, but now I do a lot less damage when I use that discipline so I'm scared that I won't be able to keep aggro. What should I do? =)<br>
<br>
